Summary: Limited shell for secure file transfers
Name: scponly
Version: 4.6
Release: 3
License: GPL
Group: System Environment/Shells
URL: http://sublimation.org/scponly/

Source: http://sublimation.org/scponly/scponly-%{version}.tgz
